  "dev": "vite",
  "build": "vite build",
  "preview": "vite preview"
}


You start it with:

npm run dev

ğŸ”¹ If you see this:
"dependencies": {
  "react-scripts": "5.0.1"
}


âœ… That means your project uses Create React App (CRA) â†’
You should have:

"scripts": {
  "start": "react-scripts start",
  "build": "react-scripts build",
  "test": "react-scripts test",
  "eject": "react-scripts eject"
}


You start it with:

npm start

